            </div>

            <div class="character">
                <span class="character-name">PROFESSOR LOGIC:</span>
                <div class="dialogue">(tie completely <span class="tie-malfunction">askew</span> for the first time ever) "I... I must conclude that optimal cognitive performance requires both logical operations AND broader reasoning processes. The quantum duck represents... a logically valid model for understanding cognitive flexibility."</div>
            </div>

